 * team.member_2_role => 成员2职位:text:Policy, trust, and table checks
 * team.member_3_icon => 成员3头像:text:PD
 * team.member_3_name => 成员3姓名:text:Table Operations
 * team.member_3_role => 成员3职位:text:Room flow and access planning
 * team.member_4_icon => 成员4头像:text:CO
 * team.member_4_name => 成员4姓名:text:Content Desk
 * team.member_4_role => 成员4职位:text:Guides, updates, and player copy
 *
 * group:cta => 底部CTA
